        <mxCell id="title3" value="Entra ID Integration — Progress State" style="text;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;html=1;fontSize=20;fontStyle=1;align=center;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="40" y="20" width="1520" height="40" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="col1" value="✅ DONE — on origin/master" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=14;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="40" y="80" width="500" height="780" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="c1" value="commit 33a4e7d&#xa;Least-privilege refactor&#xa;&#xa;• EnableUserLookup toggle added&#xa;• User.ReadWrite.All removed from&#xa;  requiredResourceAccess&#xa;• 6 narrow permissions wired 1-to-1&#xa;  with feature toggles&#xa;• Sentinel labels now include labelType:User&#xa;• CRITICAL → High severity mapping&#xa;• Cross-RG workspaceResourceId fix&#xa;• conditional Entra credentials&#xa;• Microsoft Sentinel branding" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="60" y="130" width="460" height="200" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="c2" value="commit 4dd0535&#xa;v1.1.0 GitHub release + ARM URL fix&#xa;&#xa;• FunctionApp.zip (23K) attached to release&#xa;• ARM WEBSITE_RUN_FROM_PACKAGE now&#xa;  points to v1.1.0 (was v1.0.0 which&#xa;  never actually existed on GitHub)&#xa;• Customer Deploy to Azure button works" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="60" y="350" width="460" height="140" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="c3" value="commit ac1eb6a&#xa;Force MFA Re-registration (Option 1)&#xa;&#xa;• EnableForceMfaReregistration toggle (off)&#xa;• actions/entra_id.force_mfa_reregistration()&#xa;• 7 authentication method types supported&#xa;• Password method always preserved&#xa;• Graceful 401/403 permission-denied handling&#xa;• 9 files touched: config.py, entra_id.py,&#xa;  function_app.py, azuredeploy.json, README,&#xa;  .env.example, deploy.sh, deploy.config,&#xa;  validate.sh" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
