        <mxCell id="p1" value="Option 2 — MSSP Multi-Tenant&#xa;&#xa;Convert app registration to multi-tenant so&#xa;one integration can act on multiple customer&#xa;Entra tenants (A manages X, Y).&#xa;&#xa;Changes:&#xa;• signInAudience = AzureADMultipleOrgs&#xa;• TENANT_MAPPING env var (domain → tenant_id)&#xa;• Per-tenant token cache&#xa;• target_tenant_id column in LAW&#xa;• new setup_multitenant_app.sh script&#xa;&#xa;Blockers:&#xa;3 product questions open (email not in mapping&#xa;behavior, multi-workspace routing, per-tenant&#xa;toggles)&#xa;&#xa;Effort: 1-2 sessions + 2-tenant E2E test" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1100" y="130" width="460" height="380" as="geometry" />
