        <mxCell id="p2" value="GitHub Actions auto-release&#xa;&#xa;Workflow that on every git tag push:&#xa;• zips production/FunctionApp/&#xa;• attaches to a new GitHub release&#xa;• tags release as the target of ARM URL&#xa;&#xa;Could then pin ARM URL to&#xa;/releases/latest/download/FunctionApp.zip&#xa;instead of a specific version.&#xa;&#xa;Nice-to-have, not blocking." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
